==English==

===Adjective===
'''irreversible'''

#[[Incapable]] of being [[reverse]]d or [[turn]]ed [[about]] or back; incapable of being made to [[run]] [[backward]]; as, an irreversible engine.
#Incapable of being reversed, [[recall]]ed, [[repeal]]ed, or [[annul]]led; as, an irreversible [[sentence]] or [[decree]].
# (''Thermodynamics'') Incapable of being reversed to the original state without consumption of free energy and increase of [[entropy]].

